{"tid":999068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑪麗醫護食蘋果　膠層繼續加人工","createTime":"2019-01-28T12:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T07:45:53.000Z","uid":12599,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1364aa03a18fa850f32a52635e1b092ddc3a88d0","tid":999068,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0_CeAsI_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0_CeAsI_1200x0.jpg&h=96c800d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲要自己去拎，過咗時間就連蘋果都冇得食，繼續「捱義氣」。（作者提供圖片）<br />\n<br />\n今日錦龍收到做醫護的學弟來圖，話佢哋在瑪麗連「魚蛋都冇得食」，只係得一個限時自行領取的蘋果，去「守護蘋安」，「打打氣」。<br />\n<br />\n學弟更說現時在病房，是每天都有同事請假不夠人工作的狀況下，床位加到爆的極限狀態。每天的工作都過載，更有同事要被要求 OT 12 小時，更要不停賣假，「CO 啦 O 啦 PH 啦 AL 啦 乜都賣得」，才能勉強「維持服務」。<br />\n<br />\n公營醫療系統人工比私營市場低而工作負荷又重，人才不斷流失。私營醫療系統一見奇難雜症又會為免負責而射上公營系統，更令公營教學醫院如瑪麗醫院收症更多。更有不少支援人員因為上班路途遙遠編更又爆時，不勝負荷而離職，更令本身已經因為流感高峯期而到達運轉極限的瑪麗醫院狀況接近崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n財爺陳茂波今日（編按：作者寫於 1 月 27 日）在 Facebook 直播中表示，預計來年財政盈餘會減少三分之二，所以要小心預算。既然政府不肯停止倒錢落海，那可否先根據這個比例，把所有司局長及醫管局高層的人工，減少三分之二，再將這些錢撥入醫療開資去增加床位和請人加人工，而不是邊叫人「捱義氣」、「食魚蛋食蘋果」，一邊繼續高床軟枕去打「輸入外地醫護人員」的算盤？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E7%91%AA%E9%BA%97%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E9%A3%9F%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C-%E8%86%A0%E5%B1%A4%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2591%25AA%25E9%25BA%2597%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C-%25E8%2586%25A0%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%258A%25A0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B7%25A5%2F&d=V%2FMePAjw%2FzabXJhWRsrUTFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=ece16e97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2591%25AA%25E9%25BA%2597%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C-%25E8%2586%25A0%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%258A%25A0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B7%25A5%2F&h=d6576ec3\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E7%91%AA%E9%BA%97%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E9%A3%9F%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C-%E8%86%A0%E5%B1%A4%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5/</a>"},{"pid":"b5b3ea8ec27680f08b590121bbf7aa8f7a203514","tid":999068,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:29:45.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"ee66e98026943fe2b7cfa37356eb2af51b46d413","tid":999068,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:30:29.000Z","msg":"集中營feel"},{"pid":"fd54ec0508d8044c3b3a60f94bb6001fd647bce1","tid":999068,"uid":53378,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"開始懷疑班高層係直線搏屌"},{"pid":"15697ad3276b96ec8a34a0694c696aa72e415500","tid":999068,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:31:24.000Z","msg":"其實今年流感高鋒期過左，件事草草了事既話，下年同樣有呢個問題發生"},{"pid":"3bbd736b8a3bb01f8377967d73b2db96c77bf700","tid":999068,"uid":232185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"一日一蘋果，醫生遠離我<br />\n咒人唔使返工定暗示俾你罷工"},{"pid":"1025b817206b3c8f6d0cca2f9e69459e6796f808","tid":999068,"uid":18635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:40:59.000Z","msg":"其實係咪激將法黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又請明星又搞小食日<br />\n痴撚線宜家又送蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1d4bedb52de7a00b67b76dfb941c8eec4c066e","tid":999068,"uid":168172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:41:58.000Z","msg":"請飯盒都唔肯 蘋果我屌你老母"},{"pid":"9b6fab3edb713c16f81889c86605afab95923c5f","tid":999068,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1025b817206b3c8f6d0cca2f9e69459e6796f808","tid":999068,"uid":18635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-